These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
3 different pets are kept: snake, cat, fish
1. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Pet     | cat    | fish       | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, lettuce, broccoli
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating lettuce is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food     | broccoli | pepper | lettuce  |
| Sport   | golf  | handball  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, comedy, action
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | epic        | action    | comedy        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, rugby, basketball
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the owner of the fish is between the person who's sport is basketball and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | basketball | rugby | skiing |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, family
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, aristoff
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action | family |
| Cigar     | pall-mall   | havana   | aristoff   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, punk, techno
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | techno | gospel | punk      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

