.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, monopoly
1. the person drinking cola is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Game       | monopoly | whist | canasta |

