The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, techno
1. the indian is on the left or right of the german##3
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the german is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Nationality           | indian | german | argentine |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco | r&b     |

