.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | water      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey       | cricket | skiing |

