.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, aconite
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk         | fanta          |
| Flower        | poppy | daisy | aconite |

