.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, journalist, engineer
There are 3 different nationalities: american, german, russian
1. the american is between the accountant and the journalist##2
2. the german is the journalist##1
3. the journalist is on the left of the engineer##1
4. the american is on the left or right of the accountant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Job      | journalist    | engineer    | accountant  |
| Nationality   | german | american | russian |

