2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the cat##2
4. the owner of the cat is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Flower   | iris | poppy | orchid |
