2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
3. the person eating broccoli is the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | traveling    | baking   | dancing |
