.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, water
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Beverage       | water    | almond-milk | lemonade  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van        | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, february
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| Birthday       | october | august | february |
| Transport   | motorbike  | roller   | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, corn
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, roller
1. the person eating cabbage is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Food          | cauliflower | corn    | cabbage |
| Transport   | roller      | snowmobile | van  |

