.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, aristoff
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | hot-chocolate | 7up         |
| Cigar   | aristoff | tiparillo  | ritmeester |

 